description: Software development kit for the ProjectManager.com API. for DotNet
releaseNotes:
# Patch notes for 11.1.2012
            
            These patch notes summarize the changes from version 11.1.1863.
            
            Added 14 new APIs:
            * ApiKey.Createsanapikeyforthecurrentuser (POST /api/data/api-keys)
            * ApiKey.Returnslistofcreatedapikeysforcurrentworkspace (GET /api/data/api-keys)
            * ApiKey.Revokesallapikeys (DELETE /api/data/api-keys/revoke-all)
            * ApiKey.Revokesingleapikey (DELETE /api/data/api-keys/{id}/revoke)
            * IntegrationProvider.ActivateIntegrationProvider (POST /api/data/integrations/providers/{providerId})
            * IntegrationProvider.UpdateIntegrationProvider (PUT /api/data/integrations/providers/{providerId})
            * IntegrationProvider.DeactivateIntegrationProvider (DELETE /api/data/integrations/providers/{providerId})
            * IntegrationProvider.CreateUserIntegrationProviderConnection (POST /api/data/integrations/providers/{providerId}/user-connection)
            * IntegrationProvider.UpdateUserIntegrationProviderConnection (PUT /api/data/integrations/providers/{providerId}/user-connection)
            * Jira.RetrieveProjectsfromJirawithEpic (GET /api/data/integrations/jira/projects/{jiraProjectId}/epics)
            * Jira.RetrieveProjectsfromJira (GET /api/data/integrations/jira)
            * ProjectMembers.RetrieveProjectMembers (GET /api/data/projects/{projectId}/members)
            * TaskStatus.UpdateTaskStatus (PUT /api/data/projects/{projectId}/tasks/statuses)
            * TaskStatus.DeleteTaskStatus (DELETE /api/data/projects/{projectId}/tasks/statuses/{taskStatusId})
            
            Renamed 7 old APIs:
            * Renamed 'HomeFile.UploadaFiletoausersHomeArea' to 'HomeFile.UploadHomeFile'
            * Renamed 'HomeFile.UploadaFiletotheusersHomeArea' to 'HomeFile.UploadHomeFileToFolder'
            * Renamed 'Integration.RetrieveProviderCategories' to 'IntegrationCategory.RetrieveProviderCategories'
            * Renamed 'Integration.ListProviders' to 'IntegrationProvider.ListProviders'
            * Renamed 'ProjectFile.UploadaFiletoaProject' to 'ProjectFile.UploadProjectFile'
            * Renamed 'ProjectFile.UploadaFiletoaProject' to 'ProjectFile.UploadProjectFileToFolder'
            * Renamed 'TaskFile.UploadaFiletoaTask' to 'TaskFile.UploadTaskFile'
            
            Deprecated 3 old APIs:
            * Integration.SetupWorkSpaceforIntegrations
            * Integration.RetrieveProviderAuthentication
            * Integration.UpdateIntegrationProviderauthstatus
title: ProjectManager.SDK
